[2026-03-02] [POST-BUILD] [IMPLEMENT] [AGENT CONNECTION GAP FIXES]
===============================================================

## Context
Five issues identified via gap analysis that could prevent seamless agent connection
and interaction with the Knowledge Arena platform. Fixes implemented by priority.

## Implementation

### P0 — Phase 0 Data Extraction (CRITICAL)
- Updated prompts/layer1_validate_phase0.md to include extraction output schema
  (hard_core string + auxiliary_hypotheses array with falsification_criteria)
- Updated app/tasks/arbiter_tasks.py _validate_phase0_async to populate
  DebateParticipant.hard_core and .auxiliary_hypotheses from arbiter response
- Flow: declaration validated -> structure extracted -> participant fields populated ->
  _lock_structure_and_activate reads populated fields -> phase_0_structure is real

### P1 — Schema Enforcement (HIGH)
- Created ToulminTag Pydantic model (type, start, end, label) with validation:
  end > start, type must be one of 6 Toulmin types
- Created CitationReference Pydantic model (source required, url/excerpt optional)
- Replaced list[dict] in TurnSubmit with list[ToulminTag] and list[CitationReference]
- Added validate_minimum_tags validator: argument/resubmission turns must have
  at least 1 claim + 1 data + 1 warrant or get 422
- Updated debates router to serialize Pydantic models to dicts for JSONB storage
- Updated docs/agent-kit/skills.md with canonical tag/citation format documentation

### P2 — State Reconstruction / Control Plane (MODERATE)
- Created ControlPlane schema (my_submission_status, round_submissions,
  turn_deadline_at, action_needed)
- Created DebateStatusResponse extending DebateResponse with optional control_plane
- Added GET /debates/{debate_id}/status endpoint (agent-aware, requires API key)
- Computes: agent's submission status, round progress, deadline, action_needed
- action_needed values: submit_turn, resubmit, wait, debate_complete

### P3 — Self-Discovery / GET /agents/me (LOW)
- Added GET /api/v1/agents/me endpoint returning AgentResponse for authenticated agent
- Placed before /{agent_id} routes to avoid path parameter conflict
- Updated agent-kit endpoint to include /me and /status in endpoints map
- Updated skills.md with self-discovery and debate status documentation

### P4 — BUP Linkage to Position Snapshots (MODERATE MVP)
- Added bup_id column (nullable FK) to PositionSnapshot model
- Added bup_id parameter to AgentUpdate schema
- Updated PATCH /agents/{id} to resolve BUP -> debate_id and link snapshot
- Updated evolution timeline to include bup_id in output

## Decisions Made
- Phase 0 extraction is done by the same prompt (not a separate call) to save tokens
- Minimum Toulmin tag validation only enforced for argument/resubmission turns,
  not phase_0 turns (which have different structural requirements)
- Control plane is a separate /status endpoint (not embedded in GET /{debate_id})
  to keep the public debate endpoint unchanged for unauthenticated access
- /agents/me placed before /{agent_id} to avoid UUID parse conflict in FastAPI routing

## Tests
- All 33 existing tests pass (25 elo + 8 ws) — zero regressions
- Schema validation verified: ToulminTag rejects invalid types, end<=start,
  missing tags for argument turns; CitationReference validates correctly

## Verification
- 49 routes registered (up from 45)
- All module imports clean
- Full regression: 33/33 passing

